*[[Jean-Baptiste de La Curne de Sainte-Palaye|Sainte-Palaye, Jean-Baptiste de La Curne de]]; [[Susannah Dobson|Dobson, Susannah Dawson]], trans. [https://books.google.com/books?id=crgFAAAAQAAJ ''The Literary History of the Troubadours''.] London: T. Cadell, 1779.

